list.abstract: wealthy（英 [ˈwelθi]，美 [ˈwelθi]），英语单词，形容词为有钱的；富有的；丰富的。短语搭配有wealthy family（富裕家庭）。例句为“But here the poor greatly outnumber the wealthy.（但是这里的穷人比富人要多。）”。 wealthy相关近义词有rich、sufficient等。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my god. She wants me out of the picture, too. Of course. Young woman meets a wealthy, older man. Who wants a kid in the way?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天呐，她也想除掉我，当然了，年轻女人遇到个富有的老男人，谁愿带个碍事的孩子呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Now Caseys aren't wealthy, they don't wanna file suit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 肖恩家里条件不是很好，他们也不打算提出诉讼。

yingyinNormal.en: What do you mean "Vastly wealthy"? Well, "Wealthy" Means a lot of money. Vastly Means even more. I'm not sure what's tripping you up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说超有钱是什么意思？有钱就是指有很多钱，加上个超就是有很多很多钱，这有什么听不懂的啊。

yingyinNormal.en: It was a resort town where the wealthy would go to soak up the sun.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是一个富人都爱去晒日光浴的度假小镇。

yingyinNormal.en: He taught me to think global when I was just local. He made me a wealthy man.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我还是个草根时，是他教会我目光远大，是他让我变得富有。

yingyinNormal.en: You're kidding. No. We are very wealthy. But the only difference is, we have more servants.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别逗了。真的，我家很有钱的，但跟这里唯一的区别就是，我们的仆人更多。

yingyinNormal.en: All the wealthy and beautiful people in movies ride Jet Skis. That can't just be a coincidence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电影里有钱又帅的人都骑摩托艇，这不可能是巧合。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, get this. It doesn't matter if he's showering her with gifts, because the Koothrappalis are vastly wealthy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，听好了，他给她买再多礼物也无所谓，因为库萨帕里家超有钱。

yingyinNormal.en: Because, folks, when the middle class does well, everybody does well, the wealthy get wealthier and the poor have a way up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为大家都知道，中产阶级发展好了，每个人也就好了，富人的财富更丰厚，穷人的日子更好过。

yingyinNormal.en: When you are married, you will make me the head of the royal household. Anastasia and Drisella we will pair off with wealthy lords. And I shall manage that boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你结婚以后，你要奉我为皇室之首，安娜斯塔西亚和多莉希拉也要和贵族们成婚，并由我来掌管那男孩。
